values:
I have not forgotten you my pretties but right now I am in Rome!

Will be back on Tuesday with about 1000 photos and very sore feet.

And maybe a couple of kilograms heavier. Damn you, delicious italian bread and icecream.

How is everyone?

PS: Italian men really are as gorgeous as they say ,)

This has made me so sad, I still can't believe it's true.

RIP Heath Ledger, you will surely be missed.

THE ULTIMATE SILENCE October 12, 1998



Listen to the mustn'ts, child.
Listen to the don'ts.
Listen to the shouldn'ts,
The impossibles, the won'ts.
Listen to the never haves,
Then listen close to me ...
Anything can happen, child.
Anything can be.

~ Shel Silverstein

Six years ago today, Matthew Shepard was murdered for being homosexual.

What will you do to end the silence?
